capacities is required for moral progress to be possible, and the abstract idea of moral progress need not be on moral agents' minds in the pursuit of the morally better. However, a desire for impactful moral progress, far from being a moral fetish, marks a particularly valuable moral outlook.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aExplikation. 4amoralische Verbesserung. 4amoralischer Fetisch. 4amoralisches Handeln.  aexplication.  amoral agency.  amoral fetish.  amoral improvement.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2022 Englishz978311099276208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2022z9783110992755oZDB-23-DPH0 cEPUBz97831107990190 cprintz978311079883840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110798913zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110798913zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110798913/original  a978-3-11-099276-2 EBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-117578-2 DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DPHb2022  aZDB-23-GOA